Note: While you can feel free to link to the pages on this web server at any level, without asking, we do not "exchange" links, so there is no need to mail us to tell us you've linked to our site.

Important Note

Some of the material on this web server is "indecent" by some people's standards but I fought this as a plaintiff in the recent case before the supreme court which struck down the Commuications Decency Act.

But the fight is not over. Support the Electronic Frontier Foundation and the ACLU in our fight against future bills.
